name: filename
label: Filename
description: The literal identifier for an electronic file. (NCIT:C171191 )

name: producedbysequencing
label: Produced by sequencing
description: A unique proper name or character sequence that identifies this particular nucleic acid sequencing assay. (NCIT:C171337 )

name: belongstosubject
label: Belongs to subject
description: An individual who is the subject of personal data, persons to whom data refers, and from whom data are collected, processed, and stored. (NCIT:C142495, IAO:0000136 )

name: belongstostudy
label: Belongs to study
description: Reference to the study or studies to which this file belongs. (BFO:0000050 )

name: belongstocohort
label: Belongs to cohort
description: A group of individuals, identified by a common characteristic. (NCIT:C61512 )

name: server
label: Server
description: A computer which provides some service for other computers connected to it via a network. (NCIT:C48297 )

name: filepath
label: File path
description: The specification of a node (file or directory) in a hierarchical file system, usually specified by listing the nodes top-down. (NCIT:C47922 )

name: fileformat
label: File format
description: The format of an electronic file. (NCIT:C171252 )

name: filesize
label: File size
description: The size of an electronic file in bytes. (NCIT:C171192 )

name: md5checksum
label: MD5 checksum
description: A 32-character hexadecimal number that is computed on a file. (NCIT:C171276 )

name: filestatus
label: File status
description: The condition for an electronic file relative to the current data or file processing step. (NCIT:C171193 )

name: creationdate
label: Creation date
description: The date a digital resource was created. (NCIT:C69199 )

name: alternativeidentifiers
label: Alternative identifiers
description: A backup sequence of characters used to identify an entity. (NCIT:C90353 )

name: belongstodatarelease
label: Belongs to data release
description: The act of making data or other structured information accessible to the public or to the user group of a database. (NCIT:C172217 )
